title: InClines to play Club Regent
text:
There’s no need to fall to pieces waiting for this concert, Patsy Cline fans. 

The InClines, a local tribute band that performs all of the legendary country singer’s greatest hits, have booked an afternoon show at Club Regent for Jan. 31. The local band, led by Michelle Anseeuw, will play a 3 p.m. show that day, performing the late singer’s various chart-toppers. 
Tickets start at $20, plus taxes and fees, and go on sale Friday via Ticketmaster and casinosofwinnipeg.com. Sponsored Links InClines to play Club Regent
